#: ../../../reference/simd/build-options.rst:431
msgid "Build report"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../reference/simd/build-options.rst:433
msgid ""
"In most cases, the CPU build options do not produce any fatal errors that "
"lead to hanging the build. Most of the errors that may appear in the build "
"log serve as heavy warnings due to the lack of some expected CPU features by "
"the compiler."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../reference/simd/build-options.rst:437
msgid ""
"So we strongly recommend checking the final report log, to be aware of what "
"kind of CPU features are enabled and what are not."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../reference/simd/build-options.rst:440
msgid ""
"You can find the final report of CPU optimizations by tracing meson build "
"log, and here is how it looks on x86_64/gcc:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../reference/simd/build-options.rst:443
msgid ""
"<style>#build-report .highlight-bash pre{max-height:450px; overflow-y: "
"scroll;}</style>"
